snippet.title: TOKYO GHOUL:re [CALL to EXIST] - Gameplay Trailer - PS4/PC
snippet.description:
Choose your side and take part in the war as a CCG member, Ghoul or Quinx in TOKYO GHOUL:re [CALL to EXIST]. Prepare to eat or be eaten in this co-op survival action experience, coming on 15 November 2019 on PS4 and PC!
